Referencing Inventory Hosts

*] Host Patterns :- used to specify the hosts which your play runs
   the name of the managed hosts or inventory group specifies using host patterns

   can be:-

   1] The name of single host listed in the inventory file
   2] You can use the ip address that listed in the inventory file
   3] Specify Host Using group Name
   4] you can target the ungrouped Hosts
   5] *.example.com => matches all hosts ended with .example.com
   6] datacenter*   => matches all hosts started with datacenter
   7] List of hosts like lab,datacenter1 . comma separated
   8] use ! to exclude any host or group
   9] 'lab&datacenter1' = > list all hosts that belong to the 2 groups


